item.title: 4.3 关注项目
item.description: 关注项目 # ngx_http_lua_module # openresty/lua-nginx-module ngx_http_lua_module - Embed the power of Lua into Nginx HTTP Servers. This module is a core component of OpenResty. If you are using this module, then you are essentially using OpenResty. Turbo.lua # kernelsauce/turbo Turbo is a framework built for LuaJIT 2 to simplify the task of building fast and scalable network applications. It uses a event-driven, non-blocking, no thread design to deliver excellent performance and minimal footprint to high-load applications while also providing excellent support for embedded uses.
